<Layout title="Shipping — saasuluk" description="saasuluk shipping policy — instant digital delivery, physical-goods shipping times and rates, and order tracking.">
  <h1>Shipping</h1>
  <p class="tag">A starter policy — replace it with your real terms before launch.</p>
  <h2>Digital delivery</h2>
  <p>Licenses and downloads are delivered <b>instantly</b>. The moment your order is confirmed you'll get a receipt by email, and everything you bought is available in <a href="/dashboard/s/orders">your orders</a> — no shipping required.</p>
  <h2>Physical goods</h2>
  <p>Physical items ship within <b>1–2 business days</b>. Standard delivery is typically 3–7 business days depending on your location. You enter your shipping address at checkout, and it's saved on your order.</p>
  <h2>Rates</h2>
  <p>Shipping is calculated at checkout based on your order. Digital-only orders are always free to deliver. We'll show the exact total before you pay — no surprises at the end.</p>
  <h2>Tracking</h2>
  <p>When your order ships you'll get a confirmation email with any tracking details, and the status updates in <a href="/dashboard/s/orders">your orders</a> (pending → paid → shipped).</p>
  <p style="margin-top:24px">Need help with an order? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> or check our <a href="/returns">returns &amp; refunds</a> policy.</p>
</Layout>
